### List users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

### Get user + addresses (aggregate)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1

### Create user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dana.lin@example.com",
  "firstName": "Dana",
  "lastName": "Lin"
}

### Update user
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice.nguyen@example.com",
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Nguyen-Smith"
}

### Add address to user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/3/addresses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Home",
  "street": "5 Orchard Road",
  "city": "Singapore",
  "state": "",
  "postalCode": "238838",
  "country": "Singapore"
}

### Update address
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/1/addresses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Home",
  "street": "221C Baker Street",
  "city": "London",
  "state": "",
  "postalCode": "NW1 6XE",
  "country": "United Kingdom"
}

### Delete address
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/1/addresses/2

### Delete user (cascades addresses)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/2
